headline: Citizens Financial Group Announces First Quarter 2025 Earnings Conference Call Details
summary: PROVIDENCE, R.I., March 19, 2025--As previously announced, Citizens Financial Group, Inc. (NYSE: CFG) will report its first quarter 2025 earnings on April 16, 2025. The news release and supplemental materials will be available at http://investor.citizensbank.com. CFG management will host a live conference call that morning with details as follows:
